data.description: Beautifully remodeled 3 bedroom 2 bath home with an absolutely gorgeous kitchen.  Home features hardwood laminate floors throughout, modern lighting, stylish kitchen cabinets, a beautiful backsplash, and stainless steel appliances. The lovely backyard is flat, fenced in, and features a storage building.  This house is ready to be called home!  Eligible for 100% USDA financing.
